%package     -n uvcdynctrl
Summary:        Command line interface to libwebcam
Group:          Productivity/Multimedia/Other
License:        GPL-3.0+
Requires:       udev

%description -n uvcdynctrl
Libwebcam provides a user-space library for interaction with the uvcvideo
